title: Rushworth town celebrations for Australia Day

pars: The Rushworth & District Australia Day celebration will take place on the Village Green commencing from 5 pm on Tuesday 26 January, 2021.
The BBQ previously cooked by the Rushworth Lions Club will next year be provided by the Rushworth Football/ Netball Club.
The meal will be served between 6 pm and 7 pm, followed by the offi cial part of the evening.
The Australia Day Ambassador will be Neil Thomas from The Great Aussie Beer Shed in Echuca.
The entertainment will again be ‘Type Two’ band, who did a great job last year. For your own comfort, please bring chairs, rugs and snacks and enjoy the evening.
As a reminder, fl yers will be placed in windows around town, as there will not be another edition of Waranga News published prior to 26 January, 2021.
Should you have any further enquiries please contact Gail Corner 58561379 or Mary Beck 58561474.
